.Dd February 2, 2011
.Dt KYUA 1
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm kyua
.Nd Kyua testing framework (command-line tool)
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Pp
.Nm
is the command-line interface to the Kyua testing framework.
.Pp
The canonical documentation for the tool lives in the GNU Info system.
To access the full documentation for the utility, just type one of the
following:
.Bd -literal -offset indent
$ info kyua
$ info -d __INFODIR__ kyua
.Ed
.Pp
If you are here because all you want to know is how to run the tests in
.Pa __TESTSDIR__ ,
you most likely want to read the
.Xr tests 7
manual page instead.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr info 1 ,
.Xr atf 7 ,
.Xr tests 7
.Sh AUTHORS
For more details on the people that made
.Nm
possible and the license terms, run:
.Bd -literal -offset indent
$ kyua about
.Ed
